<p>Hey friends â€“ hereâ€™s a guitar lesson teaching you how to play the Johnny Cash song â€œRing of Fireâ€ from 1963 (orig. written by June Carter and Merle Kilgore). In this tutorial Iâ€™ll teach you how to play the chords, strumming, and explain how to mimic that Mariachi horn sound with your acoustic guitar (tab included). Typically, Johnny Cash played this with his full band, benefiting from their drum / bass / electric guitar â€“ but this lesson will teach you how to play the distinctive lead riff while strumming at the same time â€“ which roughly approximates the sound of multiple instruments. Check it out and enjoy!</p>

